<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV1">
<l>poyniṉṟa ñāṉamum pollā voḻukku maḻukkuṭampu</l>
<l>minniṉṟa nīrmai yiṉiyā muṟāmai yuyiraḷippā</l>
<l>ṉenniṉṟa yōṉiyu māyppiṟan tāyimai yōrtalaivā</l>
<l>meyniṉṟu kēṭṭaru ḷāyaṭiyēṉ ceyyum viṇṇappamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
So that now we won’t have this persistent nature of knowledge 
based on falsehood, evil conduct and a filthy body, you who have been born, 
being in all the wombs you stayed in to care for the beings, lord of the unblinking ones, 
standing [there] in person gracefully listen to the supplication made by me, [your] servant.
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
